类 AbstractAlgorithmConfiguration

java.lang.Object
eu.andredick.configuration.AbstractAlgorithmConfiguration
直接已知子类:
AlgorithmConfiguration_Greedy, AlgorithmConfiguration_GreedyProbabilistic, AlgorithmConfiguration_Randomwalk, AlgorithmConfiguration_self, AlgorithmConfiguration_Stigmergy, AlgorithmConfiguration_StigmergyElite, AlgorithmConfiguration_StigmergyHeurist, AlgorithmConfiguration_StigmergyHeuristElite, AlgorithmConfiguration_StigmergyHeuristEliteLocal, AlgorithmConfiguration_StigmergyHeuristLocal, AlgorithmConfiguration_SubsetPairs
public abstract class AbstractAlgorithmConfiguration extends Object
用于配置ACO算法不同组件的抽象模板
它包含一个要填充派生类的参数列表.
用于实现实例化并返回已配置算法的 create（） 方法,
以便它可以在此类之外执行.
